	<h1>Work Experience</h1>
<p>

While my extended history is for the most part unknown, due to my status
 of being a baby. I still have a few accomplishments in the times of recent.
 Kuiil(pictured) was my caretaker during my adoptive fathers invasion of Nevarro, during this battle 
 I managed to assist in the escape of my father and his friends. Additionally, when we were back on
  the planet of Arvala-7 I saved my dad from the Mudhorn in order for him to retrieve "The Egg", which was used to escape the planet.
</p>	
